+(a^2+exp(log(a)^2+@xp1*log(a)+log(c2))+c2)^2+exp(log(a^2+exp(log(a)^2+@xp1*log(a)+log(c2))+c2)^2+@xp1*log(a^2+exp(log(a)^2+@xp1*log(a)+log(c2))+c2)+log(c2))
