"Humbert's Cubic""Hyperbolic Cosinusoid""Hyperbolic Cotangentoid""Hyperbolic Sinusoid""Hyperbolic Tangentoid"\
"Ikeda""Ilhem-Amel 1""Ilhem-Amel 2""Isoptic Cueve""Jiang""Kampyle of Eudoxus"\
"Kaplan-Yorke""Kappa Curve""Khovanov-Luchinsky""Kieroid""Kiss Curve""Klein Quartic""Knot""Kolmogorov-Volterra"\
"Kulp Quartic""Latoocarfian""Lemniscate of Bernoulli"\
"Lemniscate of Booth""Lemniscate of Gerono""Lemniscate of Montferrier""Lennard-Jones Potential""Limacon of Pascal""Limit Cycle""Links Curve"\
"Lissajous Curve""Lissajous Quadratic""Logarithmic Lemniscate""Logarithmic Sinusoid""Lozi""Lozi Mod""MacMillan""Maltese Cross"\
"Marotto-Lorenz""Martin""Maynard Smith""Mira 1""Mira 2""Multifold Henon""Nephroid"\
"Nephroid of Freeth""Newton's Diverging Parabola""Newton's Egg""Nodal Curve""OM1""OM2""OM3""OM4""OM5""OM6""OM7""OM8""OM9""OM10"\
"OM11""OM12""OM13""OM14""OM15""OM16""OM17""OM18""OM19""OM20"\
"OM21""OM22""OM23""OM24""OM25""OM26""OM27""OM28""OM29""OM30""OM31""OM32""OM33""OM34""OM35""OM36""OM37"\
"OM38""OM39""OM40""OM41""OM42""OM43""OM44""OM45""OM46""OM47""OM48""OM49""OM50""OM51""OM52""OM53""OM54""OM55""OM56""OM57""OM58"\
"OM59""OM60""OM61""OM62""OM63""OM64""OM65""OM66""OM67""OM68""Oblique Astroid""Oblique Bifolium"\
"Oblique Cappa""Oblique Cissoid""Oblique Conchoid""Oblique Pancappa""Oblique Parabolic Folium""Oblique Strophoid""Oblique Trifolium"\
"Oblique Versiera""Ophiuride""Oscillating Chemical Reaction""Parabolic Folium""Pearl of the Fourth Order 1""Pearl of the Fourth Order 2"\
"Pearls of Sluze""Pendulum""Pendulum Morozov""Polyharmonic Pendulum""Polyod of Circle""Polyod of Straight Line Parallel to Polar Axis 1"\
"Polyod of Straight Line Parallel to Polar Axis 2""Popcorn""Provenzale-Balmforth""Pseudoversiera"\
"Quadratix of Hippias""Quadratix of Tschirnhausen""Quartic Egg Curve""Right Strophoid""Satchel""Spiric Curve""Spiric of Perseus""Spiric Sections"\
