"Hoerl Curve""Holditch Curve 1""Holditch Curve 2""Humbert's Cubic""Hyperbola""Hyperbola 2""Hyperbolic Cosecantoid""Hyperbolic Cosinusoid"\
"Hyperbolic Cotangentoid""Hyperbolic Secantoid""Hyperbolic Sinusoid""Hyperbolic Tangentoid"\
"Hyperelliptic Curve""Illumination Curve""Inverse Nephroid""Isoptic Curve""Kampyle of Eudoxus"\
"Kappa Curve""Kepler's Folium""Kiepert Curve""Kieroid""Kiss Curve""Klein Quartic""Kulp Quartic"\
