"Deltoid 1""Deltoid 2""Devil's Curve 1""Devil's Curve 2""Dipole Curve""Double Egg"\
"Dumbbell Curve""Duplicatrix Cubic""Durer's Conchoid 1""Durer's Conchoid 2" \
