"Kiepert Curve""Kieroid""Kiss Curve""Klein Quartic""Kulp Quartic""Lemniscate of Bernoulli" \
"Lemniscate of Booth""Lemniscate of Montferrier" \
"Limacon of Pascal 1""Limacon of Pascal 2""Lissajous Curve 1" \
"Lissajous Curve 2""Lissajous Quadratic""Logarithmic Lemniscate""Logarithmic Sinusoid" \
"Mascheroni’s Curve""Neile's Semi-Cubical Parabola""Nephroid" \
"Nephroid of Freeth""Newton's Diverging Parabolas 1""Newton's Diverging Parabolas 2" \
"Oblique Astroid""Oblique Bifolium""Oblique Cappa""Oblique Cissoid" \
"Oblique Conchoid""Oblique Estrofoide""Oblique Pancappa""Oblique Parabolic Bifolium""Oblique Strophoid 1" \
"Oblique Strophoid 2""Oblique Trifolium""Oblique Versiera""Ophiuride""Orthoconchoid" \
"Oval of Münger""Panestrofoide""Parabola 1""Parabola 2""Parabola 3""Parabolic Trifolium" \
"Pear-Shaped Quartic""Pearl of the Fourth Order 1""Pearl of the Fourth Order 2" \
"Pearls of Sluze""Polyod of Circle""Polyod of Straight Line Parallel to Polar Axis 1" \
"Polyod of Straight Line Parallel to Polar Axis 2""Power Exponential Curve""Pseudoversiera""Pursuit Curve 1" \
"Pursuit Curve 2""Quadratix of Hippias""Quadrifolium" \
