"Semi-Trident""Serpentine Curve""Spiric Curve""Spiric of Perseus""Spiric Sections" \
"Superellipse 1""Superellipse 2""Syntractrix""Szego Curve""Teardrop Curve""Tetracuspid""Toric Section""Torpedo Curve""Tractrix" \
"Trident""Trifolium 1""Trifolium 2""Trisectrix of Delange""Trisectrix of Maclaurin" \
"Tschirnhaus' Cubic""Virtual Parabola""Visiera""Viviani's Curve""Wassenaar Curve""Watt's Curve""Weibull Curve""Windmill Curve"
